Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion out of all activity executions in the event log
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion across all cases
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' activities

Name: Percentage of variants that start with SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all cases

Name: Number of times SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion is immediately followed by Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' activities for cases where activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' occurs

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion occurrences that are not followed by SW-Checklist Completed within 7 days
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all cases where 'SW-Checklist Completed' does not happen

Name: Ratio of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to SW-Checklist Completed across the entire log
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Percentage of cases where SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion appears more than once
Metric: the average of the function base > 1 where base is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion'

Name: Frequency of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion in cases that eventually lead to SW-EIC Reject
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' activities for cases where activity 'SW-EIC Reject' occurs

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion occurrences that precede any reviewer-related activity (e.g., SW-Reviewer Agreed, SW-Reviewer Declined)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Number of variants containing SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion that result in a final decision of SW-EIC Accept
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' activities for cases where activity 'SW-EIC Accept' occurs

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion events that occur before any plagiarism check activity (Plagiarism Originality Report Completed or Plagiarism Percent Match Threshold Exceeded)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Frequency of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion in comparison to Manuscript Export Succeeded
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' activities for cases where activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' occurs

Name: Percentage of cases where SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion is followed by a checklist reminder activity (e.g., SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days or SW-Checklist Completion now due)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days'

Name: Number of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion instances that are part of variants ending in withdrawal or rejection (e.g., Manuscript is Withdrawn, SW-EIC Reject, SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit)
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' activities for cases where activity 'Manuscript is Withdrawn' occurs

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion occurrences that are directly succeeded by Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission'

Name: Ratio of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation across all traces
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Frequency of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion in long-running variants (performance > 1,000,000 seconds)
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' activities

Name: Number of times SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion occurs without being followed by any AE assignment activity (e.g., SW-Awaiting AE Assignment or SW-AE Assign Reviewers)
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' activities for cases where activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' does not occur

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion events that appear in variants involving multiple revision cycles (i.e., containing both SW–Major Revision and RW–Major Revision activities)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all cases

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion that occurs in cases where the performer is SYSTEM and sender is onbehalfof@manuscriptcentral.com (as per log metadata)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all cases
